data.description: Remodeled and Meticulously maintained home on Large Corner lot with fully fenced large backyard. Newer Vinyl windows, New Hardy Backerboard Siding, underground sprinkler system. This fully renovated home has upscale appliances, Quartz Counters, new lighting, original hardwood floors, custom kitchen cabinets and new tile kitchen and bathroom floors. Primary bedroom has walk-in closet. RV Parking plus ample space for other vehicles plus nice one car garage. Backyard Storage Shed for all your garden tools. Large Patio with Pergola. Home is larger than it looks a must see to appreciate.
